{"tid":810424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深井嘉頓麵包廠房三級火　逾400人疏散","createTime":"2018-09-08T03:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T13:44:26.000Z","uid":35420,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"400a6827da18b74caccbf4e105ed87aa47f8bc3a","tid":810424,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T03:32:17.000Z","msg":"【11:11】消防員正動用兩條喉及四隊煙帽隊灌救，暫未接獲受傷報告。<br />\n<br />\n【10:43】現場消息稱，7樓製作鬆餅的生產線首先起火，廠房內400名職員全部需要暫停工作疏散。 <br />\n<br />\n深井深慈街一號嘉頓麵包廠房，今早(8日)8時48分發生火警，大廈冒出濃煙及火光，消防員接報到場，開動一條喉及派出兩隊煙帽隊灌救，至早上9時51分升為三級火警，期間，多人需要疏散暫避，消防正調查起火原因。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180908/mobile/bkn-20180908092255389-0908_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180908%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180908092255389-0908_00822_001.html&d=9xv0JFbQRmkqdytgjbZEH5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=acc9e56b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180908/mobile/bkn-20180908092255389-0908_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1999a82dad8fb0735b12f83777cf31fd81fac89d","tid":810424,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T03:33:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3202f60b0118340d91bff915e263ba625708b3","tid":810424,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T03:34:41.000Z","msg":"消防加人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41101af9f062049c889543757ee40b0a1101d700","tid":810424,"uid":61280,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T03:36:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>逼遷定R保險搬廠？？？</strong></span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa0d9756aac217e56509a529ddb3b3d2dda7565","tid":810424,"u